snippet.title: Gob! by st33d — gameplay (17411 high score)
snippet.description:
Found a cool little turn-based shooter from 2017 made for the 7-day Roguelike Challenge. Like most roguelikes, it gets devilishly hard towards the later levels. This is the furthest I managed to get.

Played on July 20th on the 1.2 web version.

Game: https://st33d.itch.io/gob
